column12: The epitope N 234-242 for the nucleocapsid protein of Sin Nombre virus was defined by the authors by investigating CD8+ (HLA-class I) T cell responses of infected patients.
The epitope N 127-141 for the nucleocapsid protein of Sin Nombre virus was defined by the authors by investigating CD8+ (HLA-class I) T cell responses of infected patients.
Epitopic region determined by Western Blot analysis of N-terminal and C-terminal truncations of FCV N protein.
The epitope N 367-381 for the nucleocapsid protein of Sin Nombre virus was defined by the authors by investigating CD4+ T cell responses of infected patient.
The epitope sequence was conserved in Sin Nombre virus (SNV), New York virus (NYV) and El Moro Canyon hantavirus (ELMCV).
